title: NIN Everything funny Unofficial video
description: So there was this really funny video set to the new NIN song Everything. It featured Carlton Banks dancing & Trent Reznor on a unicorn. The video was going viral until it was pulled down. Rumor has it that Trent was not a fan & that he even blocked the person who made it on Facebook. I heard all of this via my NINternet friends online. Not entirely sure how much is true but regardless, here is the video for those who didn't get to see it! I ripped it straight from YouTube.
